instructions: Put the dinner plate in the center of the table cloth.
Put the salad plate on top of the center of the dinner plate.
Put the napkin on top of the center of the salad plate.
Put the wine glass on the top right of the tablecloth.
Put the water glass on the bottom right of the wine glass.
Put the salad fork on the bottom left of the tablecloth, with the prongs pointed upwards.
Put the dinner fork on the right of the salad fork.
Put the dinner knife on the right side of the dinner plate.
Put the soup spoon on the right of the dinner knife.
